title: MNF Recap & Buy/ Sell Extreme Teams
itunes:title: MNF Recap & Buy/ Sell Extreme Teams
description:
A room filled with some heroes- Dan Hanzus, Gregg Rosenthal and Colleen Wolfe recap the Cowboys big win over the Eagles before buying or selling teams with extreme starts (such as a team 0-3 or 3-0). We preview the TNF game with a special message from one of the Wesselings - Colleen travels to Cincy!

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
